			title: "Welcome to the Frontier"
			subtitle: "Every journey starts here"
			description: [
				"§ePress E§r to open your inventory, then click the reward chest."
				""
				"§fYou have arrived in §6Arcane Frontiers§f — a world built around four pillars"
				"§fthat feed into each other: magic, technology, exploration, and colony."
				""
				"§7Your starter rewards:"
				"§7• §eWorn Notebook§7 — your complete §6Ars Nouveau§7 magic guidebook."
				"§7  Keep it in your hotbar. It auto-fills as you unlock new spells."
				"§7• §eBread ×16§7 — enough food to get through the first few nights."
				"§7• §eCompass§7 — upgrade it to a Nature's Compass in the quest below."
				""
				"§eAbout this quest system:§r"
				"§7• Press §eP§7 to open the quest book at any time."
				"§7• Quests guide — they do not force. You can explore freely."
				"§7• §6Gate quests§7 (hexagon shape) unlock the next chapter when complete."
				"§7• §6★ Integration quests§7 require progress in multiple chapters at once."
				"§7• Rewards are bonuses — you can progress without them."
				""
				"§a► This quest unlocks all other Chapter 0 quests simultaneously."
				"§a► Chapter 0 quests run in parallel — complete them in any order."
			]
			dependencies: []
		}
