			description: [
				"§6Xaero's Minimap§f displays a live corner minimap with waypoints,"
				"§fmob dots, player positions, and cave mode when underground."
				""
				"§eCore controls:§r"
				"§7• §eB§7 = Place or manage waypoints."
				"§7• §eY§7 = Open Minimap settings (zoom level, mob display, rotation lock)."
				"§7• Minimap position: configurable — drag it to any corner of your screen."
				""
				"§eWaypoints in detail:§r"
				"§7• Press §eB§7 to open the waypoint menu → click §eNew§7."
				"§7• Name it something useful: 'Home', 'Nether Portal', 'Colony Hill'."
				"§7• Assign a §ecolour§7 and §eicon§7 — named waypoints appear as"
				"§7  coloured markers floating in the world at distance."
				"§7• Waypoints are shared automatically with §6Xaero's World Map§7."
				"§7• In multiplayer, use §eShare§7 to send a waypoint to all family members."
				""
				"§eCave Mode:§r"
				"§7• The minimap detects when you go underground and switches to §eCave Mode§7."
				"§7• Cave mode shows horizontal terrain slices, updated as you move."
				"§7• §6Alex's Caves§7 biomes become navigable with Cave Mode."
				"§7• Configure the underground detection depth threshold in §eY§7 → settings."
				""
				"§eMob dots:§r"
				"§7• Red dots = hostile mobs. White dots = passive. Yellow = neutral."
				"§7• Toggle mob display on/off in §eY§7 → minimap settings."
				"§7• Disable if TPS is tight — mob tracking has a small client cost."
				""
				"§a► Task: Press B, create a waypoint named anything. Mark complete."
			]
			dependencies: ["000A0001"]
		}
