				"§fSleep through your first night in a bed."
				""
				"§eCrafting a Bed:§r"
				"§7• Recipe: 3× §eWool§7 (any colour, top row) + 3× §eWood Planks§7 (bottom row)."
				"§7• The wool colour determines the bed colour — all are functionally identical."
				"§7• Place the bed indoors with at least 2 clear blocks above it."
				""
				"§eWhen can you sleep?§r"
				"§7• Right-click the bed after §esunset§7 (the sky darkens to dusk colours)."
				"§7• On a multiplayer server: all online players must sleep simultaneously"
				"§7  to skip the night — or one player uses a §6Sleeping Bag§7 (Comforts)"
				"§7  which skips the night alone without needing everyone in bed."
				""
				"§eSets your respawn point:§r"
				"§7• Sleeping in a bed sets your §espawn point§7 to that bed's location."
				"§7• If you die, you respawn at the last bed you slept in."
				"§7• §6Sleeping Bags§7 (Comforts, see below) §cdo not§7 change your spawn."
				"§7  Use Sleeping Bags for expeditions; keep your home bed for your spawn."
				""
				"§7This quest detects the vanilla §6Sweet Dreams§7 advancement automatically."
				"§7You do not need to manually mark it — it completes when you sleep."
			]
			dependencies: ["000A0001"]
