				"§7• §eSort Upgrade§7 — press R with backpack open to auto-sort all items."
				"§7• §ePickup Upgrade§7 — auto-collects items matching the filter from ground."
				"§7• §eRestock Upgrade§7 — refills empty hotbar slots from the backpack."
