				"§eUsing the Cooking Pot:§r"
				"§7• Right-click to open the GUI (6 ingredient slots + 1 container slot)."
				"§7• Put a §eBowl§7 or §eWater Bucket§7 in the bottom-right container slot."
				"§7• Add ingredients for any recipe (search 'Cooking Pot' in JEI)."
				"§7• Heat source below = the pot bubbles and cooks automatically."
				"§7• Finished meals go into the bowl slot — right-click to collect."
				""
				"§eNew crops to find and grow:§r"
				"§7• §eTomatoes§7 — found in village farms, grow like carrots."
				"§7• §eOnions§7 — village farms, used in most savoury recipes."
				"§7• §eRice§7 — grows in water-adjacent soil, used in many stews."
