				""
				"§eCrafting a Waystone:§r"
				"§7• 2× §eLodestone§7 (top two slots) + 4× §ePolished Stone§7 (middle sides)"
				"§7  + 1× §eChest§7 (centre) + 2× §eStone Bricks§7 (bottom sides)."
				"§7• Press §eR§7 on the Waystone in JEI for exact layout."
				"§7• §6Free alternative§7: villages and §6Create: Dynamic Village§7 settlements"
				"§7  spawn Waystones naturally. Discovering one gives you a free warp point."
				""
				"§ePlacing and naming:§r"
				"§7• Place the Waystone on solid flat ground — it is two blocks tall."
				"§7• Right-click to open the naming GUI. Name it clearly:"
				"§7  'Home Base', 'Nether Gate', 'Colony Town Hall', 'Mountain Forge'."
				"§7• The name appears in every family member's teleport menu immediately."
				""
				"§eFast travel settings on this server:§r"
				"§7• §eXP cost: FREE§7 — zero levels consumed per teleport."
				"§7• §eDimensional warp: ON§7 — teleport between Overworld, Nether, End,"
				"§7  and Twilight Forest (Ch 7)."
				"§7• §eWarp Stone cooldown: 5 minutes§7 after each use of the Warp Stone item."
				"§7• §eInventory return button: NO COOLDOWN§7 — always accessible in inventory."
				""
