				"§7• Hold it → right-click → select destination → teleport."
				"§7• Carries a 5-minute cooldown per use."
				"§7• The §einventory return button§7 (Waystones UI in your inventory screen)"
				"§7  works the same way with no cooldown — use that for daily travel."
				""
				"§a► Task: Submit 1 Waystone. Craft two — place one, submit the other."
			]
