				"§7• §6One player in a Sleeping Bag skips the night for everyone§7 on the server."
				"§7  Unlike beds, teammates do not need to also sleep simultaneously."
				"§7• §eShift + Right-click§7 the placed bag to pick it back up undamaged."
				"§7• §cNever sets your spawn point§7 — your home bed respawn is always safe."
				""
